          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Sergius Stylites. The Disputation of Sergius Stylites, ofܓܘܣܝܬorܓܘܝܣܝܬwith a Jew, concerning the Sonship of Christ. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 1 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
