            <p>Vellum, about 8 in. by 5 3/8 , consisting of 79 leaves, some of which are slightly soiled and torn, especially foll. 12, 62, 63, and 73. The quires, signed with letters, are nine in number, but several leaves are wanting after fol. 1, and a single leaf after fol. 26. There are from 17 to 26 lines in each page.</p>
